  "notes": "Damian wrote this profile to mimic a shot Gabor Laczko recorded on a La Marzocco Leva machine using his Smart Espresso Profiler. He feels that this is a great profile for non milk drinks, it highlights flavours in a smooth balanced way, with a more creamy body than the thicker chocolatey body of the LRv2 profile. By Damian Brakel",
